      <div class="general__modal" id="modal01">
        <div class="general__modal-content">
          <h4 class="general__modal-title">mein ms-life</h4>
          <i class="uil uil-times general__modal-close"></i>
          <div class="general__modal-desc">
            I became the lead developer after the relaunch of the page.<br /><br
            />During this time I refactored the application to a microfrontend
            architecture to accomodate the feature requests that came after the
            relaunch.
          </div>
          <div class="spacer--buttons">
            <a
              href="https://mein.ms-life.de/"
              target="_blank"
              class="button button--small button--flex"
              >Live here<i class="uil uil-external-link-alt button__icon"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="container--flex mx-1">
            <div>
              <span class="general__modal-subtitle">Tech Stack</span>
              <ul class="general__modal-experiments grid">
                <li class="general__modal-experiment">
                  <i class="uil uil-check-circle general__modal-icon"></i>
                  <p>WordPress in headless mode</p>
                </li>
                <li class="general__modal-experiment">
                  <i class="uil uil-check-circle general__modal-icon"></i>
                  <p>GatsbyJS (SSG + SSR + CSR)</p>
                </li>
                <li class="general__modal-experiment">
                  <i class="uil uil-check-circle general__modal-icon"></i>
                  <p>Styled Components / Redux Saga / Framer Motion</p>
                </li>
                <li class="general__modal-experiment">
                  <i class="uil uil-check-circle general__modal-icon"></i>
                  <p>AR Applications</p>
                </li>
                <li class="general__modal-experiment">
                  <i class="uil uil-check-circle general__modal-icon"></i>
                  <p>Custom Backend</p>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="general__modal-subtitle">Challenges</span>
              <ul class="general__modal-experiments grid">
