          <h4 class="general__modal-title">Freestyle plus Ich</h4>
          <i class="uil uil-times general__modal-close"></i>
          <div class="general__modal-desc">
            I was in charge of a major redesign and implementing services from
            other partners.
          </div>
          <div class="spacer--buttons">
